ğŸŒ Network Configuration (Static IP)

Domain Controllers require static IP addresses.

Configured DC01 with:

Static IPv4 address (same subnet as lab network)

Subnet mask configured

Preferred DNS set to itself (loopback or DC01 IP)

Verification:
ipconfig /all


Confirmed static IP and DNS configuration.

